Package gw.api.claim

Class HistoryListFilterSet

java.lang.Object
gw.api.claim.HistoryListFilterSet
public class HistoryListFilterSet extends Object
This is the filter set for the claim history page.

Filter sets are instantiated once and shared by multiple users so they must be thread safe and must not store per user state

Author:
akeefer
